    <string name="faq_text">
        <b>HOW TO ADD A WIFI NETWORK:</b>\n\n
        Step 1: Click "Manage Saved Wifi Networks"\n
        Step 2: To save the wifi that you are currently connected to, click
            "Save Current Wifi To Favourites" or manually enter the SSID and click "Add"\n\n

        HOW TO DELETE A SAVED WIFI NETWORK:\n\n
        Step 1: Click "Manage Saved Wifi Networks"\n
        Step 2: Choose the Wifi you want to delete from the dropdown menu
        Step 3: Once selected, hit "Delete Selected Wifi"\n\n

        HOW TO CREATE NEW NOTIFICATION:\n\n
        Step 1: Click "Create New Notification"\n
        Step 2: Enter notification description\n
        Step 3: Select one of your saved Wifi networks from the options\n
        Step 4: Click Save\n\n

        HOW TO DELETE A NOTIFICATION:\n\n
        Step 1: Click "Delete Noti-Fi"\n
        Step 2: Select the Wifi network for the notification that you want to delete\n
        Step 3: Click "Delete"\n
    </string>

